synopsis.value: The tiefling leader (Zevlor, Asharak or Cerys) is sitting just on the fringes of camp, greeting us before we enter camp proper. They pretend to be thinking, but in truth they're to lead us into the centre of camp where the tieflings have prepared a surprise - each NPC holding a small globe of light that they send to join a cluster above to light the festivities. The state change for camp takes place at the first cinematic.
